name: Galacticoin #1 - The Genesis
description:
Cha-ching! Congratulations, you’ve discovered the genesis edition of Galacticoin! Collect and trade! 

!!!! To win contest for Galactible #25, you must collect before Monday, January 31, 2022 at 3:00 p.m. CST!!!!! (a screenshot of wallet addresses will be taken)

Collect as many coins as you can to be entered to win Galactible #25, the “Ruby Skull of Nibiru!” Each coin (edition) equals one entry. 5 coins = 5 entries (meaning your wallet address will appear on the list 5x). The more entries the higher chance of winning! One wallet address will be randomly chosen (using Luckydraw.me). The winner will receive an airdrop of Galactible #25. 

All remaining Galacticoins of this genesis edition will be burnt once the drawing is done and you may collect and trade them as you wish!

*additional Galacticoins will be minted in the future but numbered accordingly*

These are the ONLY #1 genesis tokens! 

Follow @galactibles on twitter for winning announcements.

GOOD LUCK!

Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations, sound effects, and music made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2022 | galactibles.com
